I use QEMU as the hypervisor of choice.

VM Part
Our task:
	- Install a VM with the Linux OS of your choice.
	- A disk size of 8 GB
	- One 4.2 GB partition
Network and Security
	- Setup a firewall, DOS protection
	- Add a user and give sudo premissions
	- Stop services you don't need
	- Two scripts
Web Part
	- Setup a web server
